`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Blindness
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast blindness <victim>

 This spell renders the target character temporarily blind.  This has two major
effects: it makes that target easier to hit and it makes it harder for them to
hit you.

